cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper is about a deep reinforcement learning method, specifically the Proximal Policy Optimization (PPO) algorithm. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also mentions the use of PPO in challenging tasks, which could potentially fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision) or cs.SY (Systems and Control).
